graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Component"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Python Init Container]
        Agent[Agent Sidecar<br/>Go - Batching/Logging]
        Router[InferenceGraph Router<br/>Go Service]
        ModelServer[Model Servers<br/>MLServer/TorchServe/Triton]
        LocalController[localmodel-controller<br/>Go Controller]
        LocalAgent[localmodel-node-agent<br/>Go DaemonSet]

        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|creates pods with| StorageInit
        Controller -->|injects| Agent
        Controller -->|creates| Router
        Controller -->|manages| LocalController
        LocalController -->|coordinates| LocalAgent
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ISVC[InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        Runtime[ServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InfGraph[InferenceGraph<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        LLM[LLMInferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        LocalCache[LocalModelCache<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| ISVC
    User -->|defines| Runtime
    User -->|creates| InfGraph
    User -->|creates| LLM

    ISVC -->|watched by| Controller
    Runtime -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModel -->|watched by| Controller
    InfGraph -->|watched by| Controller
    LLM -->|watched by| Controller
    LocalCache -->|watched by| LocalController

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>Serverless Platform]
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>Traffic Management]
        KEDA[KEDA<br/>Event-driven Autoscaling]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS Certificates]
    end

    Controller -->|creates| Knative
    Controller -->|creates| Istio
    Controller -->|creates| KEDA
    Webhook -->|TLS certs| CertManager

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integrations"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model Metadata]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS]
    end

    Dashboard -->|manages InferenceServices| Controller
    Controller -->|references models| ModelRegistry
    ModelServer -->|secured by| ServiceMesh

    subgraph "External Storage"
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    StorageInit -->|downloads models| S3
    StorageInit -->|downloads models| GCS
    StorageInit -->|downloads models| Azure

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ISVC fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Runtime fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InfGraph fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLM fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GCS fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Azure fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
